import View from "./view"; import icons from "/src/img/icons.svg"; class ShowRecipe extends View { _parentElement = document.querySelector(".recipe"); _errorMessage = "We cloud not found recipe.Please try another one!"; renderHandler(handler) { ["hashchange", "load"].forEach((ev) => window.addEventListener(ev, handler) ); } _generateRecipe() { return `
${ this._data.cookingTime } minutes
${ this._data.servings } servings

Recipe ingredients

    ${this._data.ingredients .map((ing) => { return `
  • ${ing.quantity}
    ${ing.unit} pasta
    • `; }) .join("")}

How to cook it

This recipe was carefully designed and tested by ${ this._data.publisher }. Please check out directions at their website.

Directions
`; } _generateIngredients(ing) { return `
  • ${ing.quantity}
    ${ing.unit} pasta
    • `; } } export default new ShowRecipe();
